  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Health Workers Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project as defined in the Terms of Reference (ToR) is to strengthen the capacities of local health workers in responding to health emergencies in identified technical areas through specified and pre-determined training as detailed below. The sustainability of the training will be increased by offering Training for Trainers who will be able to continue after the programme has finished. In addition Merlin will ensure that administrative  technical  logistic and documentation requirements in the conduct of the trainings are adequately addressed and reported on.</narrative>
  </description>
